# AMLGym: benchmarking action model learning
<!-- Define badges -->
<div style="display: flex; gap: 10px;">
   
  <a href="https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT" target="_blank">
    <img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-green.svg" height="20"/></a>
    
